title: 01/14/21 DPS Hour 3 Charles Barkley and Nick Wright

description:
Charles Barkley tells Dan that he still thinks that the Big 3 in New Jersey will not work. Charles says he cant wait to see this experiment and how far it goes. Nick Wright tells Dan that Aaron Rodgers has the most pressure on him to win it all.
